data.description: Don't Miss Out! Split bedroom with breakfast bar that opens to the breakfast dining, living room and formal dining area. All appliances in the home including the washing machine and dryer will stay. Great entertaining area in the backyard. Mounted TV on porch and pergola with room for a table or just a place to lounge. Only a three-minute walk to the private community pool! Seller is offering $2,500 in concessions for a buyer to use anyway they would like.
